{"tid":1515543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"臨翻外國讀書前有嘢同你地講","createTime":"2019-08-29T07:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T09:25:48.000Z","uid":255628,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"78c728c5b6c7ef30f74fbeb0de725e7e73c4bb06","tid":1515543,"uid":255628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:58:59.000Z","msg":"晨早訂左9月1機票翻加拿大多倫多讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老實講 作為一個土生土長嘅香港人<br />\n我真係無心情離開呢個屋企🇭🇰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁啱知道個日搞和你塞<br />\n慶幸個日我係朝早機 受嘅波及應該唔太大<br />\n<br />\n個日好多frd都翻去<br />\n但係佢地有啲唔好彩係晏晝機<br />\n有啲就開始抱怨 話點解要個日搞<br />\n之後我都嘗試安撫佢地叫佢地體諒下<br />\n我地作為香港人一定要為呢場運動著想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我想講<br />\n我並唔係反對咁多位搞集會<br />\n而係非常支持你地作出嘅努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算我班機係晏晝 跟住飛唔到<br />\n我一樣唔會怪責咁多位 一齊和你塞埋又點話<br />\n為作呢場運動  再多嘅不合作運動都係必須<br />\n<br />\n我呢一走<br />\n就會走兩年<br />\n等我下次翻黎嘅時候<br />\n唔知香港仲會唔會係嗰個熟識嘅樣貌<br />\n如果可以嘅話<br />\n我會留守係呢個屋企 同你地繼續抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"c7060c3c9c4f5cb853f3fe821e62c02a1e1f33ef","tid":1515543,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DhhYaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DhhYaU.jpg&h=54caa31d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b660d46bc45e26c0f0dd406fcb09fdc5f45752fe","tid":1515543,"uid":172287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:00:55.000Z","msg":"放心 我嚟緊返香港接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01481944ba18635e9f891c3dbbef6897b8ec48d3","tid":1515543,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:02:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n